name: Psychsonmaker
tagline: A GUI tool to create a BadUSB stick (based on Psychson)
body:
### How to use it?
![](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/19540127/15786569/a0428b0e-29bd-11e6-992d-1aaf00a40b25.png)
1. Download the tool here (Direct Github link)
1. Unzip the content somewhere
1. Start PsychsonMaker.exe
1. Follow the instructions

###... More is coming soon ...

So actually I don't really know how to name this project. I named it PsychsonMaker because the Flash utility this tool is using is named Psychson. But any other suggestions are welcome :)

If you find any errors in the Github config, please notify me in the issues. This is my first Github project and I don't know yet how to create a project the right way.

And last: I'm not an english prof. I can't either write good in english, nor form correct sentences. So please dont expect a perfect description, wiki or documentation.

### Copyright notes
These tools are integrated in this programm:

* Psychson by brandonlw (github page)
* Duckencode by hak5darren(github page)
* SDCC (sourceforge)
* Firmware (by a russian page, I dont remember)
